00:31:25.980 --> 00:31:27.260
Bakit hindi ka maging mas tapat?

00:31:28.020 --> 00:31:30.220
Ano ba talaga ang hinahabol mo?

00:31:32.540 --> 00:31:33.380
Sabihin mo sa akin.

00:31:34.460 --> 00:31:35.940
Baka matulungan kita.

